

1: highlighted.png + un_highlighted.png: ->
includes image resources for full and empty Stars icons


2: made a files, custom_ratingbar.xml.
See the below code and file in the drawable

            <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>

                <layer-list xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">

                <!-- Empty heart for background -->
                        <item android:id="@android:id/background"
                         android:drawable="@drawable/un_highlighted_star" />

                <!-- Full heart for progress -->
                        <item android:id="@android:id/progress"
                        android:drawable="@drawable/highlighted_star" />
                </layer-list>


4: inside value file val/strings.xml
                 <style name="CustomRatingBar" parent="Widget.AppCompat.RatingBar">
                       <item name="android:progressDrawable">@drawable/custom_ratingbar</item>
                       <item name="android:minHeight">75dp</item>
                       <item name="android:maxHeight">85dp</item>
                 </style>



5: The Layout XML ratingbar_layout.xml :

                 <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
                 <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
                     xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
                     android:layout_width="match_parent"
                     android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                     <RatingBar
                         android:id="@+id/dialogRatingBar"
                         style="@style/CustomRatingBar"
                         android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                         android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                         android:layout_gravity="center"
                         android:numStars="5"
                         android:stepSize="0.5"
                         tools:layout_editor_absoluteX="16dp"
                         tools:layout_editor_absoluteY="16dp" />

                 </LinearLayout>

